   <ul>\
      <li>\
         \pard\plain<$Scr_Ps::0>\f0\fs28\sb240\
            <term>Thermistor</term>: a type of temperature-sensitive resistor whose electrical resistance changes significantly with temperature. It is commonly used in electronic devices and temperature control systems.\
	\
\pard\plain<!$Scr_Ps::0>\f0\fs28\sb240\cf3
      </li>\
